{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"29a826a5c8","title":"对民建方针指示的精神","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cd8c390fb7","index":0,"year":1952,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"29a826a5c8"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1949-1957卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"34f6da599a","type":"title","text":"对民建方针指示的精神","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"29a826a5c8"},{"id":"dac76c2f60","type":"paragraph","text":"一、私人资本在中国建设上是有贡献的，只要不让它向坏的方面发展。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"29a826a5c8"},{"id":"83c27249fe","type":"paragraph","text":"二、不能让资本家光是图私人的利，必须兼顾国家的利，工人的利。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"29a826a5c8"},{"id":"c9557ba7a3","type":"paragraph","text":"三、很好的团结他们、教育他们、改造他们，先学习并实行共同纲领。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"29a826a5c8"}],"page":{"id":"811432a2c4","publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"29a826a5c8","start":54,"end":54}}}},"__N_SSG":true}